measurements.description: Exhibitor and hybridizer Pierre Pujol, Cymbidium Samurai Spirit, a hybrid of Cymbidium Eastern Bunny and Cymbidium erythraeum, recongnized for high diversity of color, form and size; exhibiting the species charm of erythraeum, 14 plants exhibited, two were previously awarded for quality.
